{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "7555a304-da15-4931-9835-4829a1c36404",
    "name": "Science1-09-Super Gluey",
    "sceneId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "5504e645-0932-4b44-90a9-675976b41968",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "46663537-c9c8-49de-894d-31cfd56507ae",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "e0ebcee9-5542-496c-88c6-08ce5d7ce403",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Today, we're going to explore vaporization, condensation, and the process of distillation. This process uses an alembic and retorts to separate out mixtures and thus isolate key components.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "abf5a6ad-e18e-4a16-abb1-28bcc692bcf0",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Distillation is the process used to produce Brandy from wine...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "1",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "18be6881-4571-42b6-9eee-99bb217a19aa",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, we will be focusing on a more practical and useful substance to distill - Gooey!",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "2",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "ec8c0409-812f-4881-8066-24d8e601065f",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Through the Science of distillation, we will reduce and concentrate our Gooey to turn it into a more effective adhesive. I call this substance - \"Super Gluey!\"",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "630ac23d-4064-4d0b-8d4f-d58912958a9b",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "With ordinary Gooey, a creature with the mass of an average human that steps on a pool of Gooey upon the floor will be adhered for a short time. Anything larger than a human will be unaffected by the Gooey.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "3305af68-a346-45d3-815e-692082f8c3b2",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "However, once we refine the Gooey into Super Gluey, a large monster stepping upon a pool of Super Gluey will adhere to the floor for several minutes.",
                    "emotion": "1",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fa62d138-b8b2-435c-a394-cd38116e346b",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "After the monster gets loose from the Super Gluey, his feet, hooves, or tentacles continue to stick to the floor, impeding its movement for several more minutes.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4846a6b4-c940-4d01-b6c3-64fe23687e90",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions before we begin the distillation demonstration?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "60d0f1d1-2021-42fc-bcea-a88f0bbf4bf3",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "30af16e1-b598-4e57-ab7b-ccd8055321fd",
                            "text": "Talk About Brandy",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "bcf8666e-a3ea-4ba0-b46f-a630bc8fe4bc",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7a7f833a-ec43-429c-84f8-4f7a9b9e29ce",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "Maybe you could show us how to distill wine into brandy as the initial demonstration before we get to the Super Gluey part... I mean, it seems like a good way to clean the equipment...",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f33744be-be0c-466d-8301-bac8399f6591",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "And then we'd be able to taste the effect distillation has upon wine, in the interest of Science, of course.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "99a19b96-6e94-4641-badb-66ed48585155",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "39c5360f-b3f3-4b69-9878-5cf454921193",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Excellent suggestion!",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "013a3e37-3698-4db6-a073-62b54e24c5d2",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Unfortunately, the distilling process for Gooey is a lengthy process. We need to get started immediately if we want to make Super Gluey before class is over.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "2",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "11b0ed43-261d-4d02-b752-2fc2073930e2",
                            "text": "Ask About Super Gluey",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "e42b275c-2731-4525-8642-930951cce1f5",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6e7f920a-282e-413f-ba46-acc6fed15fa7",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "What happens if a large monster steps in the Super Gluey, and after it gets free, steps into the same pool of Super Gluey again? Is the Super Gluey used up the first time, or will it work again?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "04e55d1a-051f-42cc-8e5b-4f97cce4111c",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "19b6ded3-1c8c-4b2c-8f40-69b6f50e14b9",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Very good question! I have no idea whether or not there will be enough Super Gluey left on the floor to be effective after a monster has stepped on it.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "547258f4-0f6f-49bc-b98b-5b4191ab7546",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Which means, young man, that you will have to experiment with the Super Gluey with an actual monster to find out! I look forward to seeing your research on the subject.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d57465e6-0790-42b0-8277-988e92151d4a",
                            "text": "Make a Joke",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "d515ba12-a43d-4f4d-b5e3-ddc30e4b18dd",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "33",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "08a06f1b-5945-4cfa-8c7a-f55e7e0b9c64",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "I was going to make a pun about using <i>de still</i> to do distillation, but I figured you'd just give me an angry <i>retort.</i>",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "0554601d-b70f-4f40-9f2f-05cd9d0bfa25",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6ac1ac57-996d-4230-a2ba-7e6b572b0214",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I am <i>still</i> waiting to hear the <i>condensed</i> version of your distillation joke, but it seems to have <i>vaporized.</i>",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "548a5a3a-3815-4424-9d4e-92deac3dcbe5",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeInventory",
                    "id": "4c3c5984-d600-47e6-9b20-07b69ba03a78",
                    "propId": "7835cc20-43ad-41ed-b6fb-5c4b3a49599d",
                    "sceneId": "a2508b7e-a177-4a96-93bd-4d8ab88dffc4",
                    "change": "1",
                    "count": 1,
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "1fa5e6cb-0ce4-46fd-a306-f5285e0859c6",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "It takes three doses of Gooey to make one dose of Super Gluey. Today, I shall be supplying enough Gooey for you all to make 3 doses of Super Gluey. In the future, you will have to create your own Gooey before you can make Super Gluey.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                    "id": "37df8063-328b-476a-9960-675213728266",
                    "name": "Sticky Situation",
                    "notify": true,
                    "description": "Today, we distilled Gooey to make Super Gluey. The stuff is supposed to stick monsters to the floor and then make them slow down afterwards. How tacky."
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "04c1ecbb-c0df-4087-ad4f-42743fb77516",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "We begin by putting the Gooey into a retort and then apply heat...",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                    "id": "37762e1d-3c4e-4913-a651-c5b9fd58d923",
                    "scope": "scene",
                    "scopeId": "4c80661d-0537-46d4-b6d6-422313186fac",
                    "scopeFilterId": null,
                    "tagsToAdd": "GotSuperGluey",
                    "tagsToRemove": null
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}